Additional Restrictions:

It is strictly prohibited to modify, alter, or create derivative versions of the Bible text content included in this software.

This includes but is not limited to:
- Changing the wording of scripture texts
- Removing or altering verses
- Replacing or editing translations
- Repackaging modified biblical content as part of any application or service

The Bible text content must remain unchanged and used only in its original, unmodified form as provided in this software.

These restrictions apply only to the included software and its packaged content, not to public domain source texts outside this project.
